What the Table Columns Mean

Word: A word that rhymes with poppy%27s.

Rhyming Percentage: How closely the word rhymes with poppy%27s. A 100 means perfect rhyme while an 80 or 90 means a close rhyme. When this column says "Slant Rhyme," the word only rhymes if said in a certain way.

Syllables: The number of syllables in the word.

Type: The type of word.
